  <summary date="2020-12-08T13:50:08Z" status="Introduced in House">This bill extends the statute of limitations for civil and criminal violations of federal campaign finance laws.

Specifically, it extends the statute of limitations for civil violations from 5 years to 15 years, and for criminal violations from 5 years to 10 years.</summary>
